<span id="freeTextContainer15036088542958291285">I agree with J. If the original reviewer really wants to understand Christianity, then the best thing to do is go right to the source, the Bible. Whil</span>
  <span id="freeText15036088542958291285" style="display:none">I agree with J. If the original reviewer really wants to understand Christianity, then the best thing to do is go right to the source, the Bible. While I am a fan of Lewis’ work, his words are certainly not going to be perfect, because he himself was not perfect. But the Bible is God breathed and ordained, and is what any person seeking a relationship with God should refer to.</span>
